caption: @taylorswift I know I am a bit late but it’s been one year since your trial and I just wanted to say that I am so proud of you for standing up for every one who has ever been sexually assaulted and harassed. Your soul is so brave and your truth is strong enough to sustain this harsh and dense reality. I hope you know that whatever comes up you are strong enough to transcend and master it, you have already made it through so much and it is so inspiring to see that you still have a strong divine intention and you still give from an abundant heart, what comes back to you will always be healthy and nourishing. Thank you for empowering yourself for creating lasting change for the rest of the planet. I love you.
